Title: Establishes parity in reimbursement rates for supportive stabilization services provided that are substantially equivalent to crisis stabilization center services
Summary: Establishes parity in reimbursement rates for the first twenty-four hours of supportive stabilization services provided that are substantially equivalent to crisis stabilization center services.
ActClause: AN ACT to establish parity in reimbursement rates for supportive stabilization services provided that are substantially equivalent to crisis stabilization center services
